FeedPackage.Description: The package is intended to help generate various sequences, random and with rules. Provided is Sequence class, that given min, max and step can calculate, without enumerating, such basic descriptives as sum, length, Variance, Standard Deviation etc. or enumerate lazily all elements. Also, extension methods to generate random sequences can be found in GetSequence class.

FeedPackage.Description: Craig's Utility Library is one of the largest collections of utility classes and extension methods for .Net. It includes code to help with tasks including encryption, compression, serialization, file management, email, image manipulation, SQL, various file formats (CSV, iCal, etc.), randomization, validation, math related classes, various data types, reflection, code gen, events, code profiling, etc.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: This version is a complete rewrite of the current system. This will break all of your code, so don't update unless you're a brave soul.
FeedPackage.Summary: This adds support for NLog as the logger that the library uses
FeedPackage.Title: CUL.NLog
